{"tid":935371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本政府決定將華為及中興產品　排除出採購清單","createTime":"2018-12-10T03:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T03:18:56.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"29aa5e32af70e79c34203679c6a488189013c161","tid":935371,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T03:18:56.000Z","msg":"共同社報道，日本政府決定，將中國通信設備生產商華為和中興通訊的產品，排除出政府採購清單。<br />\n<br />\n日本傳媒早前引述政府消息報道，日本政府將修訂有關政府採購的內部規則，禁止政府向華為及中興通訊採購電訊產品，擔心情報洩漏及遭到網絡攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n美國早前亦禁止政府採購華為設備，澳洲及新西蘭亦以國家安全為由不准5G網絡使用華為設備。英國電信亦撤走現有3G及4G流動網絡核心部分使用的華為設備，5G核心不再使用華為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432524-20181210.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432524-20181210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=VfU7UGqeyHdBUD1vc26TcXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ed890dba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1432524-20181210.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0f5302d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1432524-20181210.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}